{"tid":985144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯邦調查局拘捕企圖用反坦克導彈襲擊白宮的男子","createTime":"2019-01-17T11:00:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T12:26:05.000Z","uid":28765,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"beb006735c3fdc76b17203e23187ad8ca3039000","tid":985144,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T11:00:30.000Z","msg":"美國聯邦調查局透過臥底行動拘捕一名男子，他計劃以反坦克導彈襲擊白宮。<br />\n<br />\n被捕男子21歲，來自佐治亞州。<br />\n<br />\n檢察部門指，去年三月收到地方執法人員通報，指疑犯變得激進，改了名字並計劃前往外地，到極端組織「伊斯蘭國」控制的地區。<br />\n<br />\n聯邦調查局派臥底人員同他接觸，疑犯透露因為沒有護照不能出境，所以將襲擊目標改為白宮和自由神像。<br />\n<br />\n疑犯星期三用自己的汽車，同臥底人員交換武器，包括槍械、爆炸裝置同反坦克導彈時被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1438507-20190117.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1438507-20190117.htm&d=3m4rN%2F1AIvPT8ELKuhEPHp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=bf280a40\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1438507-20190117.htm&h=de9a5454\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1438507-20190117.htm</a>"},{"pid":"deff27bce0055b04532079b1fbe5a6c005e33895","tid":985144,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T11:12:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d452d2128e861cbd0a01d8ba4928a2c868f72d3","tid":985144,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T10:30:38.000Z","msg":"應該等佢射完先拉  咪即時可以宣布緊急狀態起牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e345c6671dda2d4c019ecb12e242f7c915994984","tid":985144,"uid":213441,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2d452d2128e861cbd0a01d8ba4928a2c868f72d3","tid":985144,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T10:30:38.000Z"